data.description: OO Interface to the Voice-Server Teamspeak
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Maybe this Interface can be put below Speech:: or Voice::. But the
    Interface is about administrate the Server (get the status,
    registrated users etc.). other Interfaces seems to have also their
    own Namespace and I think it's unlikly, that Teamspeak will collide
    to another module.
